Task 8: Theme
Theming enables switching between different styles, like light and dark modes, by using variables.

Sass Theme Switcher Example

$light-bg: #fff;
$dark-bg: #333;
$light-color: #333;
$dark-color: #fff;

body.light-mode {
  background-color: $light-bg;
  color: $light-color;
}

body.dark-mode {
  background-color: $dark-bg;
  color: $dark-color;
}
